    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it clear whether 10 year ILR rule would be retroactive or to newcomers",
        "additional_details": "We agree its the Governments right to make new rules as they want but its our rights to plan our life. We need clarity on the new laws on settlement.\r\n\r\nMake clear the applicability of the new ILR rules specifically the 10 year rule to get ILR (applicable retroactively or to new comers)",
        "background": "Please clarify if the new ILR rules as prescribed in May 2024 white paper, specifically 10 year ILR rule would be applicable retroactively or to new comers. ",
